trans-unit.source: Represents a cell in the rendered table of a tabular ASP.NET data-bound control, such as <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en celle i tabellen gjengitte i en tabellvisning ASP.NET databundet kontroll, for eksempel <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The DataControlFieldCell class is a strongly typed <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell> class that represents a cell in ASP.NET data-bound controls that render their contents in a tabular layout, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DataControlFieldCell er en forespørselsparameter av sterk type <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>som representerer en celle i ASP.NET databundet kontroller som gjengir innholdet i en tabellvisning oppsett, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> klassen</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object that contains the DataControlFieldCell object controls how the cell is rendered by applying styles to the cell.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objektet som inneholder DataControlFieldCell objektet kontrollerer hvordan cellen gjengis ved å bruke stiler til cellen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: You can access the containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til inneholdende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objektet ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell.ContainingField%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"></xref> class, setting the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object as the cell's container.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"> </xref> klasse, angi den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objektet som den cellen beholder.

trans-unit.source: This constructor uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName> element defined by its base class to render the cell.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName>elementet er definert av basisklassen å gjengi cellen.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object passed in the `containingField` parameter is used to determine whether to show headers and what styles to apply to the cell when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekt sendt den `containingField` parameteren brukes til å finne ut om du vil vise overskrifter, og hva stiler skal brukes til cellen når den gjengis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"></xref> class, setting the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object as the cell's container.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell"> </xref> klasse, angi den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objektet som den cellen beholder.

trans-unit.source: The `tagKey` parameter is passed to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl> base class constructor, and controls the HTML tag that is emitted by the control.
trans-unit.target: Den `tagKey` -parameteren sendt til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>grunnlag for klassen konstruktøren, eller kontroller HTML-koden er slippes ut av kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> passed in the `containingField` parameter is used to determine whether to show headers and what styles to apply to the cell when it is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>sendt den `containingField` parameteren brukes til å finne ut om du vil vise overskrifter, og hva stiler skal brukes til cellen når den gjengis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"></xref> that specifies the HTML tag to render for the cell.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"> </xref> som angir HTML-koden til å gjengi for cellen.

trans-unit.source: The default tag used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell"></xref> class is <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardkode som brukes av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TableCell"> </xref> klasse <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlTextWriterTag"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> object that contains the current cell.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objekt som inneholder gjeldende celle.

trans-unit.source: The content rendering for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell> object might be affected by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> properties of the containing field, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Innhold gjengivelsen for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>objekt kan bli påvirket av de ulike <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>Egenskaper for inneholdende feltet, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ShowHeader%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ControlStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField.ItemStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCell>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> that contains the current cell, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if no <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> is passed to the class constructor.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> som inneholder gjeldende celle eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, hvis ingen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> er sendt til konstruktøren klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies whether the control validates client input.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om kontrollen validerer klienten inndata.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the control validates client input; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis kontrollen validerer klienten inndataene; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
